{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"ad710f05-6a21-4ea3-a5ff-05749cb8f8b5","content":"Your `.testsettings` file is **not supported** in modern MSTest (v3+). It must be migrated to a `.runsettings` file. Here's what your file configures and how each setting maps:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout` property (30s) | `<MSTest><TestTimeout>` |\n| Code coverage data collector | `<DataCollectors>` section |\n| Assembly resolution / deployment | Not needed in SDK-style projects |\n\nLet me create the replacement:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_013zhhiWDFeAZtqD2RifhzYp","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-57c4694a85b54619a803ca9ccd3bf1c6/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <RunConfiguration>\n    <!-- Global test timeout in milliseconds (was TestTimeout property in .testsettings) -->\n    <TestSessionTimeout>30000</TestSessionTimeout>\n  </RunConfiguration>\n\n  <MSTest>\n    <!-- Per-test method timeout in milliseconds -->\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n    <!-- DeploymentEnabled is false by default in SDK-style projects; no action needed -->\n  </MSTest>\n\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n                     uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n                     assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.dll\">\n        <Configuration>\n          <CodeCoverage />\n        </Configuration>\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-57c4694a85b54619a803ca9ccd3bf1c6/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"8eaef581-069d-4c9a-a710-13d987384bc2","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has an MSTest v3 project with a `.testsettings` file. `.testsettings` files are deprecated and not supported in 